<p><%= Date.today %></p>
<p><%= Charity.name %></p>

<p>Dear <%= @user.fname%>,</p>
<p>
  You have been outbid for the item, "<%= @item.name %>."
  Click on the link below to return to the auction site and place a new bid.
</p>
<table style="width:60%">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align:left">Item Name</th>
      <th style="text-align:left">Link to Item</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody> 
    <tr>
      <td><%= @item.name %></td>
      <td><%= link_to "Return to item", item_url(@item) %>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p>Good luck in the auction. We couldn't do this without your support!</p>
<p>Sincerely,</p>
<p>The Sponsor</p>
